s\n- ‚úì All 4 problem pages detailed with fixes\n- ‚úì Best practices scorecard (14 categories)\n- ‚úì Implementation roadmap with effort estimates\n- ‚úì Root cause analysis for each issue\n\n**File**: `2026-02-12-comprehensive-site-audit.md`\n\nReady for Cody to review and decide what to deploy."
